# 04-flutter-frontend-rules.mdc

---
description: Flutter architecture rules
globs:
- "frontend/**"
- "app/**"
---

Flutter application rules:

- Use feature-based organization.
- Separate UI from business logic.
- Keep widgets focused.
- Reuse components.
- Maintain predictable state flow.

Never:
- Put business rules inside widgets.
- Trust client validation as security.
- Duplicate backend logic.

The client consumes backend authority.
